character_info.name: Two
character_info.hint: invisible platforms are cool. (Start in Goiky)

sections.info: Two is a green non-binary number “2”, who is also the host of "The Power of Two"
sections.obtaining:
Start in [[Goiky]].  
Go to the area near [[Bell]]; there is an invisible platform path you can walk on.  
Follow the path all the way to the end, then click the invisible box to obtain Two.
